2.7 Gravity

#Galileo - Acceleration for a free falling object is

Definition (Proportional ()).

To only be off by a constant, the factor that something changes by
Used similar to an equal sign

  • All objects fall with the same acceleration, IF there's no air to slow it down

2.8 Graphing Linear Motion

Velocity can be positive or negative, we're calling north positive, and south negative. Velocity is a slope to position.
